text:
- [Narrator] Companies
across industries want

to leverage machine learning
on their collective data
to gain valuable insights
through collaboration with their partners.
However, sharing data for model training
often raises concerns
and developing privacy and access controls
to protect data and ML model IP
can be costly and time consuming.
AWS Clean Rooms ML helps you

and your partners apply
privacy enhancing controls

to safeguard your proprietary
data and ML models
while generating predictive insights

or without sharing underlying
raw data with each other.
With AWS Clean Rooms ML,
you can bring your own model
and deploy it with your partner's data

without sharing your
model or data with them.

You can also use an AWS authored
model for lookalike model

that can help you improve
accuracy by up to 36%.

From advertising to insurance,
to healthcare, and more,
companies can securely gain insights
from their collective data
in secure and collaborative ways.
Start collaborating with your partners
to train and deploy ML models

and unlock new insights
using AWS Clean Rooms ML.
(bright music)
